# Personal CLI tool overlay drop.
#
# Executables placed here are added to PATH inside agent-spawned child
# processes (see agent/tools-mcp/index.mjs PATH wiring). Use this for
# host-specific shell scripts that personal jobs/harvesters depend on
# (e.g. `aso-rank-pulse-collect`, `flight-search`).
#
# Anything you place under `_ext/` is gitignored — see .gitignore at repo
# root and docs/architecture-public-private.md.
